fields.doc_yaml:
---
consumes:
  - application/json
produces:
  - application/json
tags:
  - merchandizing

action: GET

parameters:
  - name: pageId
    required: true
    in: query
    description: PageId
    type: string
  - name: pageType
    required: true
    in: query
    description: Page Type
    type: string
  - name: userType
    required: true
    in: query
    description: user type
    type: string

responses:
  200:
    description: Returns the details of dynamic page
    schema:
      properties:
        s:
          description: success or failure code
          type: integer
        m:
          description: response message
          type: string
        d:
          description: dynamic page details
          type: object
